    v1 = 0.0

    v1 = wp.cos(wp.abs(v1))
    v1 = (0.59 / tmp)
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.79)) + ((v0 + 0.75 * tmp + 0.26) - (v1 + 0.52 / tmp + 0.84)))
